{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"9":{"eng-name":"The Chapters on Marriage","ara-name":"كتاب النكاح"}},"section_detail":{"9":{"hadithnumber_first":1845,"hadithnumber_last":2015,"arabicnumber_first":1845,"arabicnumber_last":2015}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1934,"arabicnumber":1934,"text":"حدثنا محمد بن بشار، حدثنا ابو عامر، عن زمعة بن صالح، عن سلمة بن وهرام، عن عكرمة، عن ابن عباس، قال لعن رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم المحلل والمحلل له","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih Lighairihi"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":9,"hadith":90},"chapter":{"id":33,"ara-name":"باب الْمُحَلِّلِ وَالْمُحَلَّلِ لَهُ","eng-name":"The Muhallil and the Muhallal lahu","isFirstHadith":true}}]}